name: Unidentified_stormtrooper_(trinary_system)
content: During the Galactic Civil War, a stormtrooper chased the smuggler Roark Garnet on a speeder bike through a canyon on a planet in a trinary system. The pair battled through the canyon, with the stormtrooper attempting to ram Garnet's speeder bike into the canyon wall. Garnet responded in kind, forcing the stormtroopers' bike into a crash.
